    "When they were used in GitLab CI/CD, they performed security tasks, found threats and resolved issues, all while the pipeline ran smoothly in under 3 seconds on average.The amount of latency was acceptable for the DevOps teams based on their guidelines.",
    "As many as 15 releases could be made at once across three clouds and the agents scaled up and down with Kubernetes HPA to maintain proper enforcement instantly.Table 2 Pipeline Impact Analysis CI/CD Pipeline Avg.",
